  "3316830": {
    "name": "Queen's Revenge",
    "steam_appid": 3316830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/2a4006e593f401e954e57b0abce869a5.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/2a4006e593f401e954e57b0abce869a5.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/2a4006e593f401e954e57b0abce869a5.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背叛与黑暗将女王从她的家园剥夺。被困于一个阴森的平行世界，她必须为生存而战，击败敌人并驱散黑暗——希望有一天能够夺回她应得的王位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/2a6e344391a34f05f3eb4bb4b36dbf52.avif?t=1764077544\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras_big/2a6e344391a34f05f3eb4bb4b36dbf52.avif?t=1764077544 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 <strong>Queen’s Revenge（女王的复仇）</strong> 中，你不仅仅是一个指挥官——你亲自战斗在最前线。作为女王，你需要在<strong>战略性基地建设</strong>与<strong>激烈战斗</strong>之间找到平衡。<br>🌞 <strong>白天阶段：</strong> 击败敌人并解锁新的建筑区域来扩张你的领地。每个行动都会消耗<strong>日间体力</strong>，因此请谨慎规划。<br>🌙 <strong>夜晚阶段：</strong> 抵御敌人的进攻浪潮，利用基于技能的战斗系统保卫你的城堡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合了<strong>深度战略与动态战斗</strong>，本游戏带来了独特的挑战，<strong>每个决定都至关重要</strong>。你能否抵挡黑暗的侵袭，重新夺回你的王位？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/ef7fc77feb7e7d7e4e29abe102f87608.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>游戏目前处于<strong>原型开发阶段</strong>。截图和GIF不代表最终版本——敌人死亡动画等功能仍在开发中。</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/5e50b693aa34111168ee420a06efdc45.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心策划你的防御，来对抗<strong>空中和地面单位</strong>。建造专门的防御塔，以针对不同类型的敌人——防空炮塔可以消灭飞行威胁，而强大的地面防御则能对付重装敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/090cd2391a7a6cf94129201268158e8d.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/090cd2391a7a6cf94129201268158e8d.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/090cd2391a7a6cf94129201268158e8d.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/fe540e23bfb493ceeb3854a4909e88a8.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款融合<strong>技能型直接战斗</strong>的策略动作游戏，包含闪避、格挡和精准攻击，战斗节奏与技巧决定胜负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6846f1e52abcbac960ff0d3add009847.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6846f1e52abcbac960ff0d3add009847.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6846f1e52abcbac960ff0d3add009847.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/728824b5ce3187f544b69fff2620d49b.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >争夺新的建筑区域！敌人的营地守护着宝贵的土地——在白天消灭所有敌人，即可解锁新的防御建设点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/e45e5718a204948c8172f15ee4ba37f4.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/e45e5718a204948c8172f15ee4ba37f4.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/e45e5718a204948c8172f15ee4ba37f4.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/9e9d969cf841a9664837b4d6ae136bea.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >生存于无尽的敌人浪潮之中！每到夜晚，敌人会成倍增长——明智地使用你的防御工事，并制定战略战术来保卫你的基地直到黎明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/35b0476ff71c978dcac793229065c949.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/35b0476ff71c978dcac793229065c949.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/35b0476ff71c978dcac793229065c949.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/9626a68bc962e6ec0d3f427950b3de82.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理放置<strong>墙体和障碍物</strong>，将敌人引导至杀戮区域，迫使他们通过狭窄地带，使你的防御达到最佳效果。调整基地布局，利用敌人的弱点，确保女王的生存！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6063b8534c952080c6a3ce6ef7ac146f.poster.avif?t=1764077544\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6063b8534c952080c6a3ce6ef7ac146f.webm?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/6063b8534c952080c6a3ce6ef7ac146f.mp4?t=1764077544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3316830/extras/ffff7f127e8038ec96f5739697467f3a.avif?t=1764077544\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入我们的社区！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为旅程的一部分！我希望<strong>与你们一起</strong>塑造这款游戏——你的想法、反馈和热情将帮助它变得更加出色。让我们<strong>携手打造一款真正令人惊叹的游戏！</strong> 🚀🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
